{
  "texts": [
    "This can be achieved through easily accessible privacy notices and user agreements.",
    "48 Right to be forgotten Integrate robust data management systems that allow users to request the deletion of their personal data effortlessly.",
    "Ensure that AI systems are equipped with features to permanently remove data upon request, maintaining user trust.",
    "Implement a proactive approach by continually assessing potential data privacy risks associated with AI processing.",
    "Establish a framework for regular DPIAs that lead to the timely identification of risks and the adoption of necessary mitigation strategies."
  ]
}